Config.Description:
    GeometryFriends Evolution - The goal is to create an optimal circle player.
    Individuals are evaluated for how many collectables they can pick in 10 games.

    Score/fitness = weighted sum of collectables collected + distance to target collectable + elapsed time.

	100 * normalized(collectable colledted);
	10  * normalized(distance to target collectable);
	1   * normalized(elapsed time);
